## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-102">Wystąpienie <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> jest tworzone, gdy <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> lub <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> obiekt zgłasza `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> object raises an `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-103">Aby uzyskać informacje dotyczące `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` zdarzeń, uzyskiwać dostęp do następujących właściwości w obsłudze zdarzenia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-103">To obtain information related to an `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` event, access the following properties in the handler for the event:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A> Właściwość odwołuje się do pozycji urządzenia wejściowego w jego wygenerowanego strumieniem audio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-104">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A> property references the input device's position in its generated audio stream.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-105">Z kolei <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A> właściwość odwołuje się do pozycji aparat rozpoznawania w jego wejście audio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-105">By contrast, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A> property references the recognizer's position within its audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-106">Te pozycje mogą być różne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-106">These positions can be different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-107">Aby uzyskać więcej informacji, zobacz [przy użyciu zdarzenia rozpoznawania mowy](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-107">For more information, see [Using Speech Recognition Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-108"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A> Właściwość wskazuje, jaki problem wystąpił.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-108">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A> property indicates which problem occurred.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> pochodną <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0dd60-110">W poniższym przykładzie zdefiniowano program obsługi zdarzeń, które zbiera informacje o <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0dd60-110">The following example defines an event handler that gathers information about an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> event.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the speech recognition engine.  
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the AudioSignalProblemOccurred event.  
  sre.AudioSignalProblemOccurred += new EventHandler<AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs>(sre_AudioSignalProblemOccurred);  
}  
  
// Gather information when the AudioSignalProblemOccurred event is raised.  
void sre_AudioSignalProblemOccurred(object sender, AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs e)  
{  
  StringBuilder details = new StringBuilder();  
  
  details.AppendLine("Audio signal problem information:");  
  details.AppendFormat(  
    " Audio level:               {0}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Audio position:            {1}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Audio signal problem:      {2}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Recognition engine audio position: {3}" + Environment.NewLine,  
    e.AudioLevel, e.AudioPosition,  e.AudioSignalProblem,  
    e.RecognizerAudioPosition);  
  
  // Insert additional event handler code here.  
}  
  
```
